data.description: MLS# 272131 Welcome to 1209 E 10th ave. You will instantly be in awe of this cozy yet modern home in the heart of Kennewick. The updated interior, including new flooring and paint, adds a contemporary touch, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings. With three bedrooms and a well-designed living space, this home offers the ideal environment for hosting friends and family. The large yard and shop, in combination with the appealing interior, provide a well-rounded property for those seeking a comfortable and stylish living space. Set an appointment to view this home today! New Roof, appliances, and mini split installed this year.
